h2 Buttons

p Button is for clicking, not linking.

:example
  <button class='button'>click button</button>
  <button class='button button--outline'>click button</button>
  <input class="button button--primary" type='submit' class='button' value='click submit'>
  <input type='button' class='button' value='click input button'>

:example
  <input class='button' type='submit' value='submit disabled' disabled>
  <input class='button' type='button' value='button disabled' disabled>
  
:example
  <button class='button button--primary'>button primary</button>
  <button class='button button--secondary'>button secondary</button>
  <button class='button button--round'>button round</button>
  <button class='button button--primary button--round'>button primary round</button>

p Button with all styles reset. Usefull for buttons with JavaScript-magic-onclick.

:example
  Does <button class='un-button'>this</button> look like a button to you?

h3 Button, group

